      "span_text": "One hundred three episodes of S aureus endocarditis in drug addicts were excluded because the clinical aspects of endocarditis in this subpopulation were reported in detail in 1995. Sixty-seven other cases were excluded either because no medical records were obtained (41 cases) or because the information was insufficient (26 cases)."
